1 - Not interpret unclosed quotes.
1 - Not interpret unspecified special characters ;
1 - Not interpret unspecified special characters \
0 - Have a working History.
1 - Search the right executable.
    - Check if is an absolute path.
    - Check if is in current path.
1 - Launch the right executable.
0 - Builtins.
P - Expand tokens content.
0 - “<<” read input from the current source until a line containing only the
    delimiter is seen

BUILTINS :
            0 - (1) echo    : $_
            0 - (1) cd      : $OLDPWD, $PWD, $_
            0 - (1) pwd     : $_
            0 - (1) export  : $env
            0 - (1) unset   : $env
            0 - (1) env     : $_
            0 - (1) exit    : $_, $?

